description:
The Sabbath matters not only to God, but also to God’s Remnant Church. As such, it is the mission of the Adventist Church to proclaim the Sabbath to the world. God cares about the Sabbath because He cares about us. He cares about the world. He cares about you. #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

To watch the full video, paste this link into your browser: https://youtu.be/frRurzHvaHo?si=0Cpdv9wUGjAmoTpM.
